data.text:
#115778 by gilly

Dodge DN5 700 6v53 was created by gilly

Now that the Dodge is in my custody, Interland has accepted the said vehicle for a few modifications & a bit of a tidy up. The Chocs has asked for me to allow him the privilege to make this truck, stand out a bit .

The plan is to have it ready for the Adelaide run, hopefully to give the old C a spell.

The first picture is prior to ownership change, so it will be interesting to see the changes take place.

Arrives at Interland

Tools etc gathered ready for the surgery :'(

Chocs informs me that some serious modifications have begun today, hopefully I will attend the site by the end of the week to view the progress after my work commitments

Gilly
